{
  "texts": [
    "\"But you know, when I went back, when I met them in this pub, they immediately started again.",
    "'Hey, it's old Parkers!' they all shouted.",
    "They still call me that, as though no time at all had gone by.",
    "It's old Parkers.'",
    "They actually made this big braying noise to welcome me when I first came in, oh God, I can't tell you how awful it was."
  ]
}